color:white'>2.1 </span><span style='font-family:"宋体","sans-serif";
color:white'>如果庄家胡牌或流局则下盘依然由该庄家做庄。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='text-align:left;line-height:18.0pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:"宋体","sans-serif";
color:white'>2.2 </span><span style='font-family:"宋体","sans-serif";
color:white'>如果非庄家胡牌则下一盘由胡牌玩家做庄。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='text-align:left;line-height:18.0pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:"宋体","sans-serif";
color:white'>3</span><span style='font-family:"宋体","sans-serif";color:white'>、玩法</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='text-align:left;line-height:18.0pt'><span style='font-family:"宋体","sans-serif";color:white'>游戏在一开始，只有庄家可得到十四张牌，其余的人十三张。庄家从牌中选出一张牌丢出。此时，其它三家都有权力要那张丢出的牌。庄家的下家（右手边的玩者），有权力吃或碰或杠那张牌，其它两家则只可碰或杠那张牌。<span
lang=EN-US> “ </span>碰<span lang=EN-US> ” </span>比<span lang=EN-US> “ </span>吃<span
lang=EN-US> ” </span>优先。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='text-align:left;line-height:18.0pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:"宋体","sans-serif";
color:white'>4</span><span style='font-family:"宋体","sans-serif";color:white'>、牌型</span></p>

